{
 "name": "RPlog_Morganna_s_Detox",
 "title": "Morganna's Detox",
 "summary": "Recovering in the Naval Main Medical Centre, the scarred Morganna suffers miserably through spice withdrawal, begging Admiral Adlerson to give her back the spice as she vomits and curls up in pain. Adlerson refuses firmly, insisting she see the detox through, even as she blames him for the delayed plague cure that got her hooked. The no-nonsense Chief Maelle arrives and, unintimidated by either patient or Admiral, defends her duty of care to all patients and patiently questions Morganna about her habit, offering relief without sedatives. Through their exchange Morganna opens up about her addiction's roots in the Yavin plague, and Maelle warns her honestly of the lifelong cravings ahead while encouraging her to endure.",
